descriptionHtml:
It is just a simple edit that makes Faendal look younger and like a warrior. This mod changes Faendals face and nothing more! 

 - Compatability with other mods: Yes!
 - NO other mods are required.
 - MODS USEFUL: XCE - Xenius Character Enhancement (for a better look face).

- Installation: Put the .esp and texture - meshes folder into your data folder.
- Unistall: go to data folder and delete Faendal\'s textures, meshes and esp.

Enjoy it ;) ...
author: Nephae
